    <title type="html"><![CDATA[如何运行 react16 之后测试]]></title>
    <link href="http://zhaozhiming.github.io/blog/2017/11/08/run-react-test-with-react-version-16/"/>
    <updated>2017-11-08T20:36:00+08:00</updated>
